# ML Subsystem

- Gated behind `HU_ENABLE_ML`. Use `#ifdef HU_ENABLE_ML` guards.
- Read `src/ml/CLAUDE.md` before modifying.
- Read `docs/standards/engineering/memory-management.md` — all tensors freed via allocator.
- Read `docs/standards/engineering/performance.md` — measure binary size impact.
- Vtable interfaces: `hu_model_t`, `hu_ml_optimizer_t`.
- Test gradient checks structurally (parameter existence, forward/backward success), not numerically.
- No bare `malloc` — use `hu_allocator_t`.
